                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The secret to soloing with your animation lies in the Berseker Strength line of spells.  Give your pet a weapon so it can dual wield.  Then Berserk and Haste your pet, pull with Slow, when Berserk falls off recast.  Throw in your dot early and maybe nuke when the mob gets low on health.   Experience progression will be slower than with a charmed mob, but it's a workable tactic for killing blues (works especially well with the pet/Bersek spell line upgrades at 49).  Soloing with your animation is best though when farming, where you're not concerned with exp and just want a safe way to kill light blues and greens.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><img src="http://mywpages.comcast.net/chascraw4d/images/maesig.jpg" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
