                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Bobber can serve a couple of uses, but only when ya get up to 50+.
<br />

<br />
1) Distraction or monster bait, to pull aggro off you for that fleeting second to get a rune off
<br />
2) A mana battery, you can reclaim him for a lil bit of mana
<br />
3) extra dps when the tank is a little thin, if you dont mind taking a hit to get Bob to work, tash aggro is great for this.
<br />

<br />
40-50 I would go more charm heavy but thats me, it will just make things quicker plus you learn some control tactics that are invaluable at 50+.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Blofeld, 65 Coercer, Torv</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
